{"tid":820762,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「山竹」掃過菲律賓13死 狂風暴雨捲走屋頂","createTime":"2018-09-15T15:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T03:41:04.000Z","uid":165683,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd8e26119f2a2bb96d5e89e8adc8aebe37c44f1","tid":820762,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:17:47.000Z","msg":"可唔可以將個風當玩...<br />\n<br />\n【最新進展】：<br />\n● 救援官員表示，死亡人數增至13人<br />\n● 當局證實2名協助救援的礦工、一名少年及一名少女死亡<br />\n● 「山竹」中午時掃過菲律賓呂宋北端，離開陸地進入南海<br />\n● 受斷電影響居民多達400萬人，逾10萬人入住庇護中心<br />\n● 「山竹」帶來狂風暴雨，捲走鐵皮屋頂，吹倒電線杆<br />\n● 「山竹」凌晨1時40分在呂宋北端卡加延省拔高市(Baggao)登陸，平均風力時速270公里，陣風時速更高達325公里<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180915/58683817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180915%2F58683817&d=v3Van2dSiGNBLLWy6HnaAzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1b1e795f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180915%2F58683817&h=2f1bc5db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180915/58683817</a>"},{"pid":"622a35e78de96d13fbdd42d5eeae707c4bf346ea","tid":820762,"uid":30788,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"死得13人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff200c2d7c030fc6097fcd57dd52e77e11f3911d","tid":820762,"uid":810,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"622a35e78de96d13fbdd42d5eeae707c4bf346ea","tid":820762,"uid":30788,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:26:11.000Z","msg":"死得13人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T15:29:24.000Z","msg":"1300都嫌少"},{"pid":"a48b0ff89c4a9f474bec767bb062f8ae1563702b","tid":820762,"uid":45914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"re